title: Indonesia Vegetarian Society
description: IVS (Indonesia Vegetarian Society) has been registered as a member of the International Vegetarian Union since 1999. IVS was founded with the goal as an organization to disseminate information about vegetarian life in Indonesia, develop a universal love, and save the life of the world through vegetarianism.
streetAddress: Royal Progress International Hospital Jl, Sunter Lake, North Sunter Paradise, Jakarta
